<H3> <TI>   NADK Spokesman Denies Use of Thai Territory </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BK1003070694 (Clandestine) Voice of the Great National Union 
Front of Cambodia in Cambodian 2330 GMT 9 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK1003070694 </F>
