behalf, he fully supports the Korean people's struggle for 
socialist construction and for the country's independent and 
peaceful reunification, and referred to the further development 
of friendly and cooperative relations between the two parties 
and countries. 
  The talks were held in a friendly atmosphere. After the 
talks, the CPV Central Committee hosted a banquet for the WPK 
delegation. 

