  It is ill-boding that Kim Yong-sam accompanied by brasshats 
incited the consciousness of confrontation and war fever at the 
military academies at a time when working-level contacts for the 
exchange of special envoys were underway. 
  This shows that the puppets are little interested in the 
improvement of the inter-Korean relations, but persistently 
seek only division and confrontation. 
  With the traitor Kim Yong-sam remaining in power, neither 
the 
successful promotion of North-South dialogue nor peace of the 
Korean peninsula and its peaceful reunification is thinkable. 

