  [Text] Hanoi VNA March 12 -- The Third Annual 
Vietnam-Philippines Consultative Meeting was held on March 10-11 
in Manila, the Philippines. The Vietnamese delegation led by 
Deputy Foreign Minister Vu Khoan had working sessions with the 
Philippine delegation led by its counterpart Rodofer Severino. 
