  [Text] Tokyo, March 12 KYODO -- Japanese Labor Minister 
Chikara Sakaguchi left for Detroit Saturday [12 March] to attend 
a meeting of ministers from the Group of Seven (G-7) economic 
powers on employment issues, to be held there on March 14 and 15. 
  Ministers from the United States, Japan, Germany, Britain, 
